Name: colorama
URL: https://github.com/tartley/colorama
Revision: 4ea8b1c7cbf96cc21613bb51b38fc49831fdddb4
License: BSD-3-Clause
License File: colorama/LICENSE.txt
Description:
colorama is a library to set terminal output colors. It is a cross-platform
library that should do the right thing on different host systems, and it avoids
printing ANSI escape codes to non-TTY outputs which is important for our Infra
uses.
Revision is from `git merge-base JIRI_HEAD origin/upstream/fix-ci`.
